L4. The visarga is indicated by two horizontal lines.
-->kṣiti-maṇḍāhārīya-navannaka Etat-prāveśya-
<lb
n="5"/>śāmbilakayoḫ prativāsi-kuṭumbinas samājñāpayati||<!--
L5. Two two daṇḍas are indicated by two horizontal lines.
--></p>
<p>viditam astu <pb

n="2r"/><lb
n="6"/>vo yathāsmābhi<subst><del rend="corrected">r <unclear>aya</unclear></del><add place="overstrike">r eta</add></subst>d grāma-dvayaṁ
t<choice><sic>r̥</sic><corr>ri</corr></choice>daśapati-sadana-sukha-pratiṣṭhā-karo yāva<lb
n="7" break="no"/>d ravi-śaśi-tārā-kiraṇa-pratihata-ghorāndhakāraṁ
jagad avatiṣṭhate tāvad upa<lb
n="8" break="no"/>bhogyas sanidhis sopanidhir acāṭa-bhaṭa-prāveśyas sarvva-kara-visarjji<lb
n="9" break="no"/>to mātā-pitror ātmanaś ca puṇyābhivr̥ddhaye
vāj<choice><sic>i</sic><corr>a</corr></choice>saneya-kauśika-sagotra-
<lb
n="10"/>viṣṇusvāminas tām<surplus>b</surplus>ra-śāsanenātisr̥ṣṭaḥ</p>
<p>te yūyam evam <subst><del rend="corrected">e</del><add place="overstrike">u</add></subst>palabhyāsyā<pb

n="2v" break="no"/><lb
n="11" break="no"/>jñā-śravaṇa-vidheyā bhūtvā yathocitaṁ bhoga-bhāgam upanayantas sukhaṁ prati<lb
n="12" break="no"/>vatsyatha<supplied reason="subaudible">.</supplied> bhaviśyataś ca bhūmipān anudarśayati</p>
<lg n="1" met="vasantatilakā">
<l n="a">dānād viśiṣṭam anupā<lb
n="13" break="no"/>la<add place="below">na</add>-ja<supplied reason="omitted">ṁ</supplied>
purāṇā</l>
<l n="b">dharmmeṣu niścita-dhiyaḫ pravadanti dharmma<supplied reason="omitted">M</supplied>||</l>


<l n="c">tasmā<supplied reason="omitted">d</supplied> dvijā
<lb
n="14" break="no"/>ya su-viśuddha-kula-śrutāya</l>
<l n="d">dattāṁ bhuvaṁ bhavatu vo matir eva goptu<supplied reason="omitted">M</supplied>||</l>
</lg>
<lb
n="15" break="no"/>
<p>tad bhavadbhir apy eṣā dattir anupālayitavyā<supplied reason="subaudible">.</supplied>
vyāsa-gītāṁś cātra ślokān u<pb

n="3r" break="no"/><lb
n="16" break="no"/>dāharanti||
</p>
<lg n="2" met="indravajrā"><!--
Garuḍapurāṇa 2.42.4
-->
<l n="a">agner apatya<supplied reason="omitted">ṁ</supplied> prathamaṁ suvarṇṇaṁ</l>
<l n="b">bhūr vvaiṣṇavī sūryya<lb
n="17" break="no"/>-sutāś ca gāvaḥ</l>


<l n="c">dattās trayas tena bhavanti lokā</l>
<l n="d">yaẖ kāñcanaṁ gāṁ ca mahīṁ ca da<lb
